Description:
### Inline Code

Use `code` inline for short references.

### Fenced Code Block

```javascript
// JavaScript example
function greet(name) {
  return `Hello, ${name}!`;
}
console.log(greet("World"));
```

```python
# Python example
def greet(name: str) -> str:
    return f"Hello, {name}!"
print(greet("World"))
```
